                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "One Action"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "Stride up to half your Speed. The crystals ring out with pleasant-sounding chimes that reverberate painfully in the ears of others. Each creature that you pass adjacent to during your Stride takes 4d8 sonic damage (DC 24 basic Fortitude save); a creature takes this damage only once. A creature who critically fails the save is also deafened for 1 minute.",
